title: 820-01598: No power
message: Don't think this can be repaired. i remembered during initial inspection, i saw a little liquid spill on J8500. So started checking the pins and EDP_AUXCH_N pin 2 resistance measurement come out at 2.6ohms. Pin 3 reads 58ohms.
